snippet.title: Match Village - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Match Village is a minimalist puzzle and strategy experience about matching buildings to build villages on colorful islands. Match buildings to create your villages and cities on endless islands around the world and enjoy the minimalistic and relaxing atmosphere, no resource management or armies, focus only on building.
